<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us | MoreLeads Kent</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container nav-container">
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">MoreLeads <span>Kent</span></a>
            <nav>
                <a href="index.html#what-we-do">What We Do</a>
                <a href="index.html#pricing">Pricing</a>
                <a href="index.html#about">About</a>
                <a href="index.html#faqs">FAQs</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section style="background: white; min-height: 80vh;">
        <div class="container max-width-md text-center">
            <h1>Claim Your Free Local Search Audit</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Give us 24 hours. We will review your business name, address settings, profile gaps, and tell you exactly why your local competitors are ranking higher than you.</p>
            
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/placeholder" method="POST" style="background: #F7F5F1; padding: 40px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #e5e0d8; margin-bottom: 40px;">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="bizname">Your Registered Business Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="bizname" name="business_name" placeholder="e.g. Sandwich Plumbing Services" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phone">Best Contact Mobile Phone Number</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone_number" placeholder="e.g. 07496797189" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="notes">Any Specific Competitor You Want to Beat?</label>
                    <textarea id="notes" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us if there's a specific local map profile taking your jobs..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; border: none; font-size: 1.1rem;">Submit Free Audit Request</button>
            </form>

            <div style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e0d8; padding-top: 30px; margin-top: 30px;">
                <h3>Prefer a direct phone conversation?</h3>
                <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Call directly: <a href="tel:07496797189" style="color: var(--accent-red); font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">07496797189</a></p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #707070;">Or drop inside the workshop office at Foxborough Furniture, Foxborough Hill, Eastry, CT13 0NY.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2026 MoreLeads Kent. Run alongside Foxborough Furniture.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
